                Petro<supplied reason="lost" cert="low">nia C(ai) f(ilia) Galeonis</supplied> <lb n="2"/>in fid<supplied reason="lost" cert="low">eicommisso solvendo</supplied> <lb n="3"/>Decian<supplied reason="lost" cert="low">i fratris nomine opus</supplied> <lb n="4"/>amph<supplied reason="lost" cert="low">itheatri cum ornamentis</supplied> <lb n="5"/>quod ex <supplied reason="lost" cert="low">testamento ex HS</supplied><gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/><supplied reason="lost" cert="low">fieri iusserat</supplied> <lb n="6"/>perfic<supplied reason="lost" cert="low">iendum curavit et dedicavit</supplied>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>(B): Nach CIL 11, 8023 sind 11, 5406 und 5432 zwei Fragmente einer Inschrift. Nach Gregori Fragmente von Inschriften gleichen Inhalts.</p>
